text: Lycée Jean-Vilar is a senior high school/sixth form college in Plaisir, Yvelines, France, in the Paris metropolitan area. there are 754 students; 720 of them lived in Plaisir."Etablissements." Plaisir. Retrieved on September 2, 2016. "Le lycée Jean Vilar, situé à Plaisir, accueille les postulants au baccalauréat (754 élèves dont 720 lycéens plaisirois)." ==References== ==External links== * Lycée Jean-Vilar Category:Lycées in Yvelines Category:Schools in Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines
